\id 2PE
\ide  UTF-8
\h 2 Bitru 
\toc1 2 Bitru 
\toc2 2 Bitru 
\toc3 2pe 
\mt1 2 Bitru  
\c 1
\p
\v 1 cimon Bitru bwe changa kangye bwe tomange yeecu kiriti ki nobo wo yo digyer lumar bilenkerer nawo bi yoweu mulangum ki nobo woyo diger tumar bilenkerer nawo bi yow mwor kwaamar kange nii chokka beko yeecu kiriti.  
\v 2 Luma kanga damnerem wo bi fiya yeecu nin nii cok beu a cobten dutche.  
\v 3 ki bi kwan chero cin nebo degero gwam wo dumecheu kangye yimbo wucakeu mwor nyomka kwa'amak wo cuwobo mor dugtunkak kangye tenenka chekeu.  
\v 4 mwor wuro nyeu, cin nebo norre dur nyeri nabi yilam mor nobo fiya norre mulen kwa'amar nabi cokum dor ki kaya kako kale wo cuika dikero bwir bou ti cikeu  
\v 5 ki digerowo bwiyeu, mani kambo mwa dolum tiyeu na cobten neroken ki bilen kereronindi cobten nyomka.  
\v 6 kinyom kako nin di chobten taka dorer. ki takadore konin chobten birom nerem, ki birom di chobten yimbo wucake,  
\v 7 ki yimbo wucakeu choten ki cuikanka bwitik ki chwika bwitik chobten ki cwika  
\v 8 No mulendo buro gwam wi kumendi yila duyom kumendi mani kom yila chombulome ti kaga digero bwiir mwor nyomka Teluwe bek yeecu kriti.  
\v 9 dila nii wo manki digero buro weri la weltantigti weitagye nyori cin fugma, tabum kange bwiren kerer cerowo nirom ki bwiyeu.  
\v 10 nyori kebmibo komma digero kom dollum tiye nakom nyomom chwor kumero na ti yila ce no batin ma digero birodi, mani ba yarti.  
\v 11 nure wuro nin, batin fiya doka mor liyar kwama beg kange nii fulo bew yecu kriti. nyori man nyilam ki bati kang nami kulom kumen digero biro, bwenno nyilam kom nyumom duwaleu bwenno kom tinkiti kwan dor bilenkerero kom ciko naweu.  
\v 12 nyori mannyilam ki bati kang nami kulom kumen digero biro, bwen nonyilanm kom nyumom duwaleu bwen nokom tinkibi kwan dor bilenkerero kom ciko nawu.  
\v 13 mi kwa tiri dong dong fiye mi wiyeu nomatin nomwor bwiye wurori, mi kwatiri yori kabo in kulom kimen nawo.  
\v 14 mi mwor bwiye wuroweu wori min nyu.  
\v 15 matin ma digero madullum tiyeu nanto di ki kwama wo makuberi katin kwa digero biro ki neer kang kang.  
\v 16 nyori nyi bwangtengbo yulando wo bibwe nifire bow cikeu ki kwama wo nyo yikom bikwan kange boka teluwe beko yecu kriti nyori nyon tomdur ceroki nuwe nye.  
\v 17 lacin yo dur kangye dugtanka fiye Teekwama wiyeu ki kwama wo diro bo cinen fiye dugtanka kodur wo yiki wo bwenere mi nuwa luma chek ti dutce.  
\v 18 nyo nyiki bwinyo nyin nuwam dirowo yirau dii kwama tunwo ki kwama wo nyi wari kange cwo dor bangero wucakeu.  
\v 19 la nyin wi ki ke ti dugumer, wo daten kom yoti nereu natalkireu wo ne tilang ti kumta cile nayumb de celka finikeu ri na tulkachi na ne filang mwor nere kume.  
\v 20 mordigero gwam, kom nyumom keti dugumero kangee manwo ayau ti fwetengka nii keu.  
\v 21 na cori keti dugumero kange bombo wi fye nifiro wiyeu la yuwa tanbe kwamak dici coci tok ker kwamare.   
\c 2
\p
\v 1 dila nobtomange kwama cwerke bo nobo nin kange nob meranka cwerke anbo kimen. ki an bo ketito yurangum na wuronka ce kange ci an ko teluwe ciye wo tiyen ciye. ci boti ki wuronka wulom dor ciro.  
\v 2 Ducce nawo abwanteng nure ciye, kange morece ci anko nur bilenkere wo yilam durre.  
\v 3 Morkucuno ciye ci an yuwo diger ducce kimen ki ker bi boler ciro. fuwar ciro biyeken fiye wulom. kange wuronka ciko dabo dum.  
\v 4 Nyori kwama dobbo nobtomangem ce wucare woma morkumtacile bwiranke, la nyore kwama tunken ci morkumtacile bware, naci ku, kenci luwe kumtacile tabe, kiduka ningtang bolangti.  
\v 5 Yila ci dobbo kale carko, cin yoken nufu wo meran kereti cakcakeu kange nobo niber, fiye cuwo.  
\v 6 Ci bo ki mwem wuro ka kale nobo nyombo kwama. Kwama nyori twimbi ten codome kange gomora yilam bwiyem, wuro yilam diker nunkaro fintange nobo wo nyombo kwama.  
\v 7 Na lot wo cakcake co nuwa dotange fiye nobo bwanten ner ciyer tiye, nyombo werkun nen.  
\v 8 La nii cakcake wo yim tiber cireu, kume kange kume ner cere ti kayai mor dume cakcake ce dor kekero co towe kange co nuwau.  
\v 9 Teluwe diye nyimom nure ca cokum nobkwamab ti morcuwaka kange nure ca tam nobo mani cakcake na comwe cibi diye bolange.  
\v 10 Wo bilen kere dor nobo ki dilanka bwiyek kange cwe kanka nobo Ki bi kwang keret, dor ciro kucer kange cima dike ci cwiti, maci cwatai nobdutonka.  
\v 11 Nobtomange kwama wucake wi ki bikang kange wo la ciye nyori ci bobo ki kiyange fiye teluwe diye nin.  
\v 12 Nyori bi ciro manki kwa dikeri cin maci na bii tabi biyem. ci cwekan dikero wo ci nymbe, ci anbwiyam.  
\v 13 Ci an fiye nan bwiran nangene ciye ci kwa nuwaka lima ti diye wona lima ce. dor ciro cin twelum, ci nuwo lima nangene ciye bi bolere ti, fiye cuwo ci nuwa lima ti kange kom me.  
\v 14 Ci wi ki nuwe burotum natubem, nobburokab, kero bwir mani lacine ner ci kwou nobo wo ti boyorau mornangene ciye bwiranye, nyori cin cuati ner ciro dor kucunur ci bibei cii ka.  
\v 15 Cin dubom nur bilen ke, cin ko nyori cin bwanteng nure, Balamu bi bwe Be'ore, ni wo bilan fiya ka yokka mordikero kebo cakcake,  
\v 16 Nyori yuwo weranka dor bwiran keret ce, kelba mani tok kere, weran nii tomange kwama wo twelum twele ki dir nifiret.  
\v 17 Nobo buro ci na buir man kimwem na bilor wo yuwa mwe meko yeecu cike kumtacile durwi ningtang ci ti.  
\v 18 Cin nobtokka kerek koni kange nobcwika dorek. ci bol nobo ti fiye dilanka bwiyek. cibol nobo ti, wuro cwiti naci cwam fiye nobo yimbo yorbe.  
\v 19 cin manobo nin cor ciyan cerci, ci ki bwici canga fiye bwiran ke. nyori nii cange fiye dike kwob ner cere.  
\v 20 Ni wo cerum kalenm fiye nyomka teluwe kange nii fuloka yeecu yila nyonti mor burotum bo ni neu, damcembo a cuwa bwir tiye anla kabako bwiraka.  
\v 21 La cinen diker noci nyombo nure nyime cakcake, kange wo ci nyimom di ci dubom werfundo ci ne ciye.  
\v 22 Nuka kereko wo bilenke fiye ci wiye Bicwiye yilaken kwiye ce kange ngyere yilati fiye dwiti”   
\c 3
\p
\v 1 farub mib tomange wo na yobe ce ma mulang kume ne, take gwam ciye na kulum kace na ne kom bi kwan nere  
\v 2 be na kom bulamgi ki kero nob tomange kange werfune wo teluwebe kange nii wo yafulo be nee nob tomange be  
\v 3 yomom nob buwomeb an bow diye dika kume. ciyan buwo dike ci cwiye  
\v 4 ciyan yii kom kin fee nor yilakako? ka ciko tebbebo daken dume, dikero gwam tim ka cikca kwatti ter fwelkake.  
\v 5 ci ki mantum tabum fiya no ki ker kwamar dii ko kange Bitru fiya yime mor mweme  
\v 6 take mwem wer kale, kale dim ka mwem  
\v 7 ka cikna kere, dii ko kange dor bitiner kum kira yome bi diye bolange kange werka nobo bwang ten bo kwama.  
\v 8 farub kom tabre kume win fiye Teluwebe diye nine, na coro kwini bikate, coro kwini bikate na kume wine  
\v 9 kwama tibrang bo ki norcero, nawo kangem yi ti ki. tibrang tiye, nyeu co bii ner dor mwer co cwibo kange kume a kayam, di la gwam na fiya da yiloka  
\v 10 duwal kume kwama a bo na nii kuye. dii ko a cum ki diro dur. tibitinimbo a twim ki kira. tab-tab.  
\v 11 nyori tibitininbo wo gwam anwuro, nyeu ka yila nobo wani? kom yii wucak kange cwi kwama.  
\v 12 kom ningtang diye boka kwama ko ti, diye co dii kwama an werum ki kira, tibitinimbo wuyak bwiyem kicilen kambo ken.  
\v 13 dila nor ce, bo nintang dii kwama fwirko kange dor bitinero fwirko wo nobo cak-cak a yim tiye.  
\v 14 nyori faumib, nyeu ko cwi dige wo tiyeu, dibe ko ti bati a fiya nen de ki duti mo tim cakcak kabom cem ki fowor nere.  
\v 15 take to birum nee kwama co fulokako, nawo yibe bulu mulange ki yilen do kwama ne co.  
\v 16 bulu tok dige wo mor bi fumer ceronin, wo kangem dikero wi wo bwai nyomka. fwandika kange nobo tibo fiye wine bongum digero wo na wo ci ma kangem bifumero ni neu, nur bware ciye  
\v 17 na weu farubmib kweri ka nyomom digerowo nyeu, ywelum bwi kume, kati nobo bwangten bo werfunere bol kom, lem bilenkere kume nin. la kom  
\v 18 dwi mor luma kange nyomka teluwe nii fuloka Yeecu kiritti duktangka na ce diri-diri   